body:
From UT:https://github.com/PowerShell/psl-monad/blob/master/monad/tests/monad/DRT/commands/utility/UnitTests/FormatAndOutputTests.cs#L780

below cases fail:
It "Format-Table variable with single line string for End-To-End should work"{
        $p="single line string"
        $result=$p|Format-Table -Property "foo","bar"|Out-String
        $result|Should BeNullOrEmpty
    }

```
It "Format-Table variable with multiple line string for End-To-End should work"{
    $p="Line1\nLine2"
    $result=$p|Format-Table -Property "foo","bar"|Out-String
    $result|Should BeNullOrEmpty
}

It "Format-Table variable with string sequence for End-To-End should work"{
    $p="Line1","Line2"
    $result=$p|Format-Table -Property "foo","bar"|Out-String
    $result|Should BeNullOrEmpty
}

It "Format-Table variable with string sequence for End-To-End should work"{
    $p="Line1","Line2"
    $result=$p|Format-Table -Property "foo","bar"|Out-String
    $result|Should BeNullOrEmpty
}
```
